  "notes": "Born 1506 in Sutton Valence, Kent, England — during the reign of Henry VII. The earliest known Rogers ancestor. Married Margery Gouldwell/Goldwell (1510-1552, also of Sutton Valence). Son: Francis Rogers of Dartford (1536-1568). Grandson: Sir Robert Rogers (1565-1639). Wife Margery died 1552 in Kent. Died February 4, 1555 in Sutton Valence at age 49."
